{"id":"xpoinittest-dbf112","type":"COMMENT","payload":{"id":"cmt-a394a657-41a4-4964-ad6a-5e7ee6977375","text":"## Summary\n\n- Created `src/game/board.ts` — `Board` type (`(string | 0)[][]`) and `createBoard()` factory\n- Updated `src/components/GameCanvas.tsx` — data-driven renderer with `drawBoard()` and `drawCell()` for beveled 3D tiles\n- Lifted board state into `App.tsx` via `useState`\n\n## Rationale\n\nCanvas is now a pure renderer of board state. Game logic in future stories mutates the board array; the canvas redraws via the `useEffect` dependency on `board`.\n\n## Status\n\nTypeScript compiles clean. Board renders centered with grid lines on empty cells. Ready for review."},"created_at":"2026-07-12T12:53:06.063185Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
