{"id":"xpoinittest-5220ac","type":"COMMENT","payload":{"id":"cmt-3be227ce-9b04-4c9d-ae52-e9c9a8b42783","text":"## Summary\n\n- Updated `src/hooks/useGameLoop.ts` — added `gameState` (`\"idle\" | \"playing\"`), `startGame()` action, gravity only runs when playing, player starts as `null`\n- Updated `src/hooks/useKeyboard.ts` — accepts `null` to disable input when idle\n- Updated `src/App.tsx` — shows START GAME overlay when idle, hides hint when playing\n- Updated `src/App.css` — retro neon-green button with glow, semi-transparent overlay on the board\n\n## Rationale\n\nGame state lives in the hook so App is a pure renderer. Passing `null` to `useKeyboard` cleanly disables input without extra flags.\n\n## Status\n\nTypeScript compiles clean. Game starts only on button click. Ready for review."},"created_at":"2026-07-12T13:13:41.000243Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
