{"id":"xpoinittest-bf1a50","type":"COMMENT","payload":{"id":"cmt-cf452a69-c1b9-4610-9787-8dec21edeaad","text":"## Summary\n\n- Updated `src/hooks/useGameLoop.ts` — added `softDropping` state, `startSoftDrop`/`stopSoftDrop` actions, gravity interval switches between 800ms (normal) and 50ms (soft drop)\n- Updated `src/hooks/useKeyboard.ts` — remapped controls: Space → hard drop, ArrowDown keydown → start soft drop, ArrowDown keyup → stop soft drop\n- Updated `src/App.tsx` — wired new actions, updated control instructions to show all four controls\n\n## Rationale\n\nStandard COLORBLOXX control scheme: down arrow for soft drop (hold to accelerate), space for hard drop (instant lock). Gravity interval recreates on `softDropping` state change via the effect dependency array.\n\n## Decisions made\n\n- Soft drop speed set to 50ms per row — fast and responsive while still trackable visually\n- `e.repeat` guard on ArrowDown keydown prevents re-triggering `startSoftDrop` on held key\n- Lock delay still applies during soft drop landing, only hard drop bypasses it\n\n## Status\n\nTypeScript compiles clean. All controls working. Ready for review."},"created_at":"2026-07-12T13:26:10.673194Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
