{"id":"xpoinittest-0450f4","type":"COMMENT","payload":{"id":"cmt-c9fcd1e2-2bc0-4638-85b4-0d284430516f","text":"## Summary\n\n- Added `rotate()` to `src/hooks/useGameLoop.ts` — cycles rotation index, tries current position then wall-kick offsets `[(±1,0), (±2,0)]`, integrates with lock delay reset/cancel\n- Updated `src/hooks/useKeyboard.ts` — mapped ArrowUp to `rotate`\n- Updated `src/App.tsx` — wired `rotate` into actions\n\n## Rationale\n\nSimple wall-kick table (horizontal only) suits the 4-piece set. Rotation reuses the same lock delay logic as `tryMove` — if landed after rotation, reset timer; if un-landed, cancel it.\n\n## Status\n\nTypeScript compiles clean. All rotations and wall kicks working. Ready for review."},"created_at":"2026-07-12T13:30:25.031318Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
