{"id":"xpoinittest-47804e","type":"CREATE","payload":{"description":"Engaging animations that make users want to play more. board shaking, lightning strikes, laser beams, exploding tiles, celebrations.\n\nSounds for flipping, dropping, lines disappearing. Different celebrations for 1,2,3,4 lines.","labels":["feature"],"sort_order":"a9","title":"Animations and Sounds"},"created_at":"2026-07-12T13:45:00.838387Z","created_by":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"web"}
{"id":"xpoinittest-6574d4","type":"COMMENT","payload":{"id":"cmt-1e3c834f-ad5d-484a-9ba3-f0dc04481af1","text":"## Summary\n\n- Added `score` state and `level` derivation to `src/hooks/useGameLoop.ts`\n- Extracted `lockAndScore()` helper used by both `lock()` and `hardDrop()` — awards points from scoring table after clearing lines\n- Gravity interval now level-dependent: `max(100, 800 - (level-1) * 75)` ms\n- Added `.game-layout`, `.side-panel`, `.stat` styles to `src/App.css`\n- Updated `src/App.tsx` — displays Score and Level in a side panel\n\n## Status\n\nTypeScript compiles clean. Scoring and speed progression working. Ready for review."},"created_at":"2026-07-12T13:52:00.503518Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
