{"id":"xpoinittest-f42f98","type":"COMMENT","payload":{"id":"cmt-68e98afb-0f07-481d-aebb-3dae6922eb59","text":"## Summary\n\n- Created `src/game/highscores.ts` — `getHighScores()` / `saveHighScore()` with localStorage persistence, top 10, sorted by score\n- Created `src/components/Leaderboard.tsx` — reusable table component with optional rank highlighting\n- Updated `src/components/GameOver.tsx` — two-step flow: initials input → submit → leaderboard + Play Again\n- Updated `src/App.tsx` — shows leaderboard on start screen if scores exist, refreshes after play again\n- Styled leaderboard table in `src/App.css`\n\n## Status\n\nTypeScript compiles clean. High scores persist across reloads, leaderboard displays on both game over and start screen."},"created_at":"2026-07-12T14:03:28.173789Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
