{"id":"xpoinittest-54f3b2","type":"COMMENT","payload":{"id":"cmt-34fa4608-a8e1-473c-a6ce-6b30dfb641e9","text":"## Summary\n\n- Restructured layout to 3-column: left aside (Level), center (board + overlays), right aside (Score)\n- Moved instructions below the game layout to prevent center column from stretching\n- High scores leaderboard shown on start overlay (top), START button at bottom\n- Fixed layout shift by using `visibility: hidden` instead of conditional rendering for the hint\n- Added `min-width: 100px` to asides for stable sizing\n- Cleaned up leaderboard: dropped `#` column, uniform font size/weight, Name left-aligned, Score right-aligned, Date right-aligned\n\n## Status\n\nTypeScript compiles clean. Layout is stable with no shifts between states."},"created_at":"2026-07-12T14:16:40.111089Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
