{"id":"xpoinittest-88b01f","type":"CREATE","payload":{"title":"Play Again should start the game, not return to idle","description":"## Bug\n\nAfter game over, clicking Play Again returns to the idle/start screen instead of immediately starting a new game. The player has to click START again.\n\n## Expected Behavior\n\nPlay Again should reset the board and immediately start a new game (same as pressing START).\n\n## Current Behavior\n\nPlay Again transitions to idle state, showing the start overlay with high scores and START button.","status":"PLANNED","parent_id":"xpoinittest-69a413","estimate":1,"sort_order":"a0","labels":["bug"]},"created_at":"2026-07-12T15:51:19.138659Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
{"id":"xpoinittest-5fcc95","type":"COMMENT","payload":{"id":"cmt-63f55a9d-29d6-4644-95ff-d2c1ae2c4eb7","text":"## Summary\n\n- Updated `src/game/player.ts` — `spawnPlayer` accepts optional `Tetromino` parameter\n- Updated `src/hooks/useGameLoop.ts` — added `nextTetromino` state, `lockAndScore` uses next piece and picks a new random, added `lines` counter\n- Created `src/components/NextPiece.tsx` — small 64x64 canvas preview with beveled cells, centered piece\n- Updated `src/App.tsx` — right aside: Score + Next preview; left aside: Level + Lines\n\n## Decisions made\n\n- Preview uses 16px cells (vs 30px board cells) to fit the stat box size\n- Added Lines counter to left aside for symmetric layout (user request)\n\n## Status\n\nTypeScript compiles clean. Next piece preview and lines counter working."},"created_at":"2026-07-12T15:51:47.961244Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
