{"id":"xpoinittest-88b01f","type":"COMMENT","payload":{"id":"cmt-b0b2da09-6253-4b2d-9346-5adfad6a2f37","text":"## Summary\n\nChanged `playAgain()` in `src/hooks/useGameLoop.ts` to call `startGame()` instead of transitioning to idle.\n\n## Rationale\n\nPlay Again should feel immediate — no reason to force the player through the start screen again.\n\n## Status\n\nTypeScript compiles clean. Play Again now starts a new game directly."},"created_at":"2026-07-12T15:54:28.779433Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
