{"id":"xpoinittest-385f9f","type":"COMMENT","payload":{"id":"cmt-2b96b489-c62a-46ff-8b57-11d6186c4351","text":"## Summary\n\n- Updated `src/components/GameCanvas.tsx` — switched from `useEffect` redraw to a `requestAnimationFrame` render loop reading from refs\n- Updated `src/hooks/useGameLoop.ts` — added 150ms cooldown on hard drop via `hardDropCooldownRef`\n\n## Rationale\n\nThe useEffect-based redraw had a frame delay between state change and canvas update. rAF reads directly from refs so the canvas is always in sync. The cooldown prevents a second space press from hard-dropping the next piece before the player can react.\n\n## Status\n\nTypeScript compiles clean. Hard drops render instantly, no double-fire."},"created_at":"2026-07-12T16:08:13.968471Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
