{"id":"xpoinittest-f5a6ca","type":"COMMENT","payload":{"id":"cmt-800bf6f1-376a-431a-afa3-6ab41b080c70","text":"## Summary\n\n- Added `drawGhost()` to `src/components/GameCanvas.tsx` — computes lowest valid Y, draws flat filled cells at 25% opacity\n- Ghost renders between board and player in the rAF loop\n- Hidden behind a feature flag: `localStorage.setItem(\"showGhosts\", \"true\")` to enable, off by default\n\n## Decisions made\n\n- Ghost is off by default per user preference (too easy)\n- Flag read once on module load — requires page refresh to toggle\n- Simple localStorage key `showGhosts` (no prefix needed, localStorage is per-origin)\n\n## Status\n\nTypeScript compiles clean. Ghost renders when flag is set, hidden otherwise."},"created_at":"2026-07-12T16:20:02.044791Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
