{"id":"xpoinittest-4951e7","type":"CREATE","payload":{"title":"Attract screen — falling pieces animation on idle","description":"## What\n\nWhen the game is idle (start screen), animate random pieces slowly falling in the background behind the start overlay. Pieces fall, stack, and when the board fills up, clear and restart.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] Random pieces fall on the board during idle state\n- [ ] Pieces lock when they land and stack up\n- [ ] Animation runs behind the semi-transparent start overlay\n- [ ] When the board fills to the top, clear and restart the animation\n- [ ] Animation stops when the game starts\n- [ ] No player input affects the animation","status":"PLANNED","parent_id":"xpoinittest-69a413","estimate":3,"sort_order":"a0","labels":["feature"]},"created_at":"2026-07-12T16:22:53.770536Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
