{"id":"xpoinittest-4951e7","type":"COMMENT","payload":{"id":"cmt-0861b099-34ab-46b7-8b0f-53258fadcc05","text":"## Summary\n\n- Created `src/hooks/useAttractMode.ts` — AI-driven attract screen with placement heuristic (minimizes holes, height, bumpiness; maximizes line clears)\n- AI visibly rotates, slides, and drops each piece step by step at 80ms ticks\n- Board clears and restarts when full\n- Replaced START button with \"Press Enter to Play\" pulsing text\n- Added Enter key listener to start game from idle\n- Start overlay uses gradient (opaque top → transparent bottom) to show AI playing behind high scores\n\n## Also changed\n\n- `src/App.tsx` — attract mode board/player used when idle, Enter key handler, removed bottom hint\n- `src/App.css` — gradient overlay, press-enter pulse animation, top-pinned high scores\n- `src/components/Leaderboard.tsx` — retro arcade style (gold/silver/bronze, zero-padded scores, monospace)\n\n## Status\n\nTypeScript compiles clean. Attract screen plays competently, high scores display at top, Press Enter to Play pulses below."},"created_at":"2026-07-12T16:36:50.327198Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
