{"id":"xpoinittest-3fd049","type":"CREATE","payload":{"title":"Line clear animations","description":"## What\n\nAnimate line clears with different effects based on how many lines are cleared simultaneously.\n\n## Effects\n\n- **1 line:** Quick white flash across the row before it disappears\n- **2 lines:** Flash with a brief horizontal sweep\n- **3 lines:** Tiles explode outward (particle-like scatter)\n- **4 lines (COLORBLOXX!):** Dramatic laser beam / lightning effect across all 4 rows\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] Each line clear tier has a visually distinct animation\n- [ ] Animation plays before the rows are removed and above rows shift down\n- [ ] Animation does not block gameplay (short duration, ~300-500ms)\n- [ ] Works with the rAF render loop","status":"BACKLOG","parent_id":"xpoinittest-47804e","estimate":3,"sort_order":"a0","labels":["feature"]},"created_at":"2026-07-12T16:41:25.514231Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
{"id":"xpoinittest-51f5fa","type":"CREATE","payload":{"title":"Board shake on impact","description":"## What\n\nAdd a screen shake effect when pieces land with impact — hard drops and multi-line clears.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] Hard drop triggers a brief vertical shake (~50ms, 3-4px)\n- [ ] Multi-line clears trigger a stronger shake (scales with lines cleared)\n- [ ] Shake is applied to the canvas element via CSS transform\n- [ ] Shake does not affect game logic or collision detection","status":"BACKLOG","parent_id":"xpoinittest-47804e","estimate":2,"sort_order":"a1","labels":["feature"]},"created_at":"2026-07-12T16:41:29.027786Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
{"id":"xpoinittest-f0ef89","type":"CREATE","payload":{"title":"Piece lock flash","description":"## What\n\nBrief white flash/glow on the piece cells when a piece locks into the board.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] When a piece locks, its cells briefly flash white (~100ms)\n- [ ] Flash fades back to the piece's normal color\n- [ ] Subtle enough to not be distracting but gives tactile feedback\n- [ ] Works for both gravity lock and hard drop","status":"BACKLOG","parent_id":"xpoinittest-47804e","estimate":2,"sort_order":"a2","labels":["feature"]},"created_at":"2026-07-12T16:41:32.20361Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
{"id":"xpoinittest-c52943","type":"CREATE","payload":{"title":"Celebration effects for multi-line clears","description":"## What\n\nParticle/firework effects for impressive line clears.\n\n## Effects\n\n- **3 lines:** Small burst of colored particles from the cleared area\n- **4 lines (COLORBLOXX!):** Full fireworks celebration with sparks and a brief \"COLORBLOXX!\" text flash\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] 3-line clear triggers a particle burst\n- [ ] 4-line clear triggers a full celebration with \"COLORBLOXX!\" text\n- [ ] Particles animate over the canvas then fade out\n- [ ] Effects are brief (~1 second) and don't block gameplay","status":"BACKLOG","parent_id":"xpoinittest-47804e","estimate":3,"sort_order":"a3","labels":["feature"]},"created_at":"2026-07-12T16:41:36.481252Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
{"id":"xpoinittest-9c5e73","type":"CREATE","payload":{"title":"Sound effects","description":"## What\n\nAdd 8-bit style sound effects using the Web Audio API (oscillators, no audio files).\n\n## Sounds\n\n- **Move:** Short blip on left/right movement\n- **Rotate:** Quick ascending tone\n- **Soft drop:** Subtle tick while held\n- **Hard drop:** Thud / impact sound\n- **Lock:** Click/snap when piece locks\n- **Line clear:** Ascending chime (pitch varies by line count)\n- **Game over:** Descending sad tone\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] All sounds generated via Web Audio API (no audio files)\n- [ ] Sounds are 8-bit / chiptune style (square and triangle waves)\n- [ ] Sounds are short and non-intrusive\n- [ ] Sound can be muted (localStorage flag or toggle)","status":"BACKLOG","parent_id":"xpoinittest-47804e","estimate":3,"sort_order":"a4","labels":["feature"]},"created_at":"2026-07-12T16:41:41.627473Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
{"id":"xpoinittest-fb93e0","type":"CREATE","payload":{"title":"8-bit chiptune background music","description":"## What\n\nGenerate a looping 8-bit chiptune soundtrack using the Web Audio API. Retro square/triangle wave melody that plays during gameplay.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] Background music generated programmatically via Web Audio API oscillators\n- [ ] Uses square and triangle waves for authentic 8-bit sound\n- [ ] Loops seamlessly during gameplay\n- [ ] Music starts when game starts, stops on game over\n- [ ] Does not play during attract mode / idle screen\n- [ ] Can be muted via localStorage flag or toggle\n- [ ] Tempo increases with level for added tension","status":"BACKLOG","parent_id":"xpoinittest-47804e","estimate":5,"sort_order":"a5","labels":["feature"]},"created_at":"2026-07-12T16:41:45.233249Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
