{"id":"xpoinittest-9c5e73","type":"COMMENT","payload":{"id":"cmt-3913a5d8-aa6b-40ec-82e7-5d5568926162","text":"## Summary\n\n- Created `src/game/audio.ts` — Web Audio API sound engine with lazy AudioContext init, oscillator helpers, and noise generator\n- Updated `src/hooks/useGameLoop.ts` — wired sfx calls into move, rotate, hard drop, lock, line clear, and game over\n\n## Sounds\n\n- **Move:** snappy double-blip\n- **Rotate:** ascending pitch sweep\n- **Hard drop:** bassy WHOMP with double noise bursts\n- **Lock:** sharp snap\n- **Line clears:** escalating celebrations — 1 line gets a cheerful arpeggio, 4-line COLORBLOXX gets a full two-part victory fanfare with noise bursts\n- **Game over:** long chromatic descent\n\n## Status\n\nTypeScript compiles clean. All sounds working, mutable via `muteSound` localStorage flag."},"created_at":"2026-07-12T17:00:26.985928Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
