{"id":"xpoinittest-22e3e8","type":"CREATE","payload":{"title":"Game over flow: return to attract screen after submitting initials","description":"## What\n\nAfter game over, once the player submits their initials, return to the idle/attract screen instead of showing a separate game-over leaderboard with a Play Again button.\n\n## Current Behavior\n\nGame over → enter initials → SUBMIT → shows leaderboard + PLAY AGAIN button on game over overlay\n\n## Expected Behavior\n\nGame over → enter initials → SUBMIT → saves score → returns to idle screen (attract mode + high scores + Press Enter to Play)\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] Submitting initials saves the score and transitions to idle state\n- [ ] The attract screen shows the updated high scores including the just-submitted entry\n- [ ] No separate game-over leaderboard / Play Again button needed\n- [ ] Player presses Enter to start a new game (existing flow)","status":"PLANNED","parent_id":"xpoinittest-69a413","estimate":1,"sort_order":"a0","labels":["feature"]},"created_at":"2026-07-12T17:02:03.762469Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
