{"id":"xpoinittest-22e3e8","type":"COMMENT","payload":{"id":"cmt-938e208c-98dc-42dd-abd0-ce3e99e949e3","text":"## Summary\n\n- Simplified `src/components/GameOver.tsx` — removed submitted state, leaderboard, and Play Again button. Just shows initials form, saves score on submit, calls `onSubmit` callback.\n- Renamed `playAgain` → `returnToIdle` in `src/hooks/useGameLoop.ts` — transitions to idle state instead of starting a new game\n- Updated `src/App.tsx` — `handleSubmitScore` refreshes display scores and returns to idle\n\n## Status\n\nTypeScript compiles clean. Game over → submit initials → attract screen with updated scores."},"created_at":"2026-07-12T17:03:29.072692Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
