{"id":"xpoinittest-3fd049","type":"COMMENT","payload":{"id":"cmt-2b2ad010-3357-444c-a64c-f4466a1ce35a","text":"## Summary\n\n- Created `src/game/effects.ts` — effect system with particle physics, flash/brighten/lightning renderers, and \"COLORBLOXX!\" text overlay\n- Updated `src/game/board.ts` — `clearLines` now returns `clearedRows` indices\n- Updated `src/hooks/useGameLoop.ts` — captures row colors before clearing, creates effects via `effectsRef`\n- Updated `src/components/GameCanvas.tsx` — renders active effects in rAF loop, auto-removes expired ones\n\n## Effects by tier\n\n- **1 line:** White flash fade\n- **2 lines:** Color brighten — cells glow white-hot then fade\n- **3 lines:** Flash + colored particles scatter from every cell\n- **4 lines (COLORBLOXX!):** Yellow flash, lightning bolts, particles, \"COLORBLOXX!\" text\n\n## Status\n\nTypeScript compiles clean. All line clear animations working."},"created_at":"2026-07-12T17:51:21.218216Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
