{"id":"xpoinittest-51f5fa","type":"COMMENT","payload":{"id":"cmt-ff773ec3-cb44-41e0-a5f4-d070d2ad6dd9","text":"## Summary\n\n- Added `ShakeHandle` interface and shake system to `src/components/GameCanvas.tsx` — CSS transform with per-frame decay (0.85x)\n- Added `shakeRef` to `src/hooks/useGameLoop.ts` — triggers shake on line clears scaled by count (2/4/6/8px)\n- Wired through `src/App.tsx`\n\n## Decisions made\n\n- Removed hard drop shake per user feedback — too distracting, discourages dropping\n- Shake only on line clears where it reinforces the celebration\n\n## Status\n\nTypeScript compiles clean. Board shakes on line clears only."},"created_at":"2026-07-12T18:09:22.676827Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
