{"id":"xpoinittest-fb93e0","type":"COMMENT","payload":{"id":"cmt-ecd300ca-f9e1-4c0c-a515-636210816586","text":"## Summary\n\n- Created `src/game/music.ts` — `MusicEngine` class with schedule-ahead pattern, two tracks, tempo scaling\n- **Attract theme:** Bright C major arpeggios at 150 BPM — bouncy, inviting\n- **Gameplay theme:** Grieg's \"In the Hall of the Mountain King\" (1875, public domain) in 8-bit — creeping A minor melody, tempo scales 130→220 BPM with level\n- Fixed AudioContext autoplay policy — `init()` unlocks context on first user interaction, starts pending track\n- Updated `src/App.tsx` — music state management, init on first click/keypress, tempo updates on level change\n- Renamed game to COLORBLOXX with 10 rainbow letter colors\n\n## Status\n\nTypeScript compiles clean. Both soundtracks playing, mutable via `muteMusic` localStorage flag."},"created_at":"2026-07-12T18:47:52.080202Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
