{"id":"xpoinittest-c52943","type":"COMMENT","payload":{"id":"cmt-c862c918-08ae-4d08-a895-ce76ef5efe81","text":"## Summary\n\n- Created `src/components/Fireworks.tsx` — full-viewport canvas overlay with tiered celebrations for all line clears\n- Updated `src/hooks/useGameLoop.ts` — triggers fireworks on every line clear\n- Updated `src/App.tsx` — renders Fireworks component with ref\n\n## Tiers\n\n- **1 line:** 8 sparkles drifting upward\n- **2 lines:** 12 sparkles + 6 streaks\n- **3 lines:** 2 firework bursts (15 sparks each) + 8 sparkles\n- **4 lines:** 3 firework bursts (25 sparks each) + 12 sparkles + 8 streaks\n\n## Performance\n\n- Removed `shadowBlur` (GPU-heavy) — using simple `fillRect` squares instead (fits 8-bit aesthetic)\n- Canvas sized once on trigger, not every frame\n- Reduced particle counts from original design to maintain 60fps\n\n## Status\n\nTypeScript compiles clean. Full-page celebrations working at stable FPS."},"created_at":"2026-07-12T19:22:09.856883Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
