{"id":"xpoinittest-f0ef89","type":"COMMENT","payload":{"id":"cmt-31cc2be4-b40b-4bb7-8c32-f9e4aa7ad6d2","text":"## Summary\n\n- Extended `src/game/effects.ts` — added `LockFlashEffect` type, `createLockFlashEffect()` factory, and lock flash rendering in `drawEffect()`\n- Updated `src/hooks/useGameLoop.ts` — triggers lock flash in `lockAndScore` before line clearing\n\n## Status\n\nTypeScript compiles clean. Lock flash works on both gravity lock and hard drop."},"created_at":"2026-07-13T06:02:00.448851Z","created_by":"claude-code/2.1.207 \u003cagent@mcp\u003e","on_behalf_of":"Nicolas Bettenburg \u003cnicbet@gmail.com\u003e","source":"mcp"}
